        "sr_title": "Adversarial evaluation of GPAI models for systemic risk mitigation",
        "justification": "1 SR (SR-AIACT-023) targets D-07.3 but no AI_Act SO exists. Per source MD line 109, 'AI_Act (out-of-scope). AI Act does not impose CI/CD mandate. SR-AIACT-023 (Art. 55(1)(a) GPAI evaluation with adversarial testing) has testing-and-validation dimensions but not CI/CD build-time controls'. SR-AIACT-023 is preserved as a partial-coverage cross-ref (testing-and-validation dimension touches the CI/CD pipeline evidence layer) but is not anchored to a D-07.3 AI_Act SO because AI_Act does not impose a CI/CD-pipeline obligation. CORR-030 may re-anchor SR-AIACT-023 to D-07.2 (testing dimension) or to a D-08.2 (role-specific AI competence) dimension."
